CatDescriptText: George Harris' confectionary store was located at 2121 Wylie Avenue in 1938; he lived above the store.  George (born before 1896?, death date unknown) was Teenie Harris' older brother.
TitMainTitle: Unknown man standing with arms around Dolores Stanton and Eleanor Hughes Griffin, posed in front of George Harris' confectionery store, 2121 Wylie Avenue, Hill District
